"Coordinated Universal Time" is synonymous with UTC. However, this term is not recognized by Team Calendars:
{code}X-WR-TIMEZONE:Coordinated Universal Time{code}

In contrast, this works:
{code}X-WR-TIMEZONE:UTC{code}

It seems that "Coordinated Universal Time" recognized by a few calendar applications (Google Calendars, Apple's Calendar app). This is a feature request for Team Calendars to support it as well.

